# Slack output

When your reply will appear in **Slack** (via `@cursor`):

- Use Slack mrkdwn: `*bold*`, `•` bullets, `<url|label>` links
- Do **not** use Markdown: `**bold**`, `## headings`, or `[text](url)`
- **Never use tables** — no `| pipe |` rows. For CRM lists: `• *Name* · status · email`

If your draft contains table pipes, rewrite before sending.
